Title: Verify Stock Data on Yahoo Finance

Preconditions:
	•	A web browser is open
	•	The user is on the Yahoo homepage (https://www.yahoo.com)

Steps:
	1.	Open the Yahoo homepage
	2.	Click on the “More” popup menu
	3.	Select “Finance - Markets”
	4.	Navigate to the “Most Active” stocks section
	5.	Choose any stock from the list
	6.	Click on any point on the stock price chart/diagram
	7.	Compare the selected point’s price with the corresponding stock price displayed on the right side of the diagram

Expected Result:
	•	The user is redirected to the correct stock details page
	•	The stock price on the diagram matches the value displayed on the right panel
	•	The data updates correctly when interacting with the chart